Class VehicleSignals

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.eclipse.mosaic.lib.objects.vehicle.VehicleSignals
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable
    @Immutable
public class VehicleSignals
extends Object
implements Serializable
    This class provides information about currently active signals visible to the driver. The specific signals are only set correctly if the used traffic simulator supports the values.
